OL,3,CPlans approved to make local authority
OL,4,Ca 'council of sanctuary'
OL,6,FA bid to block Cumberland Council's
OL,7,Fapplication for 'council of sanctuary'
OL,8,Fstatus has failed.
OL,10,FThe motion to block the council's bid
OL,11,Fwas rejected with 10 votes in favour
OL,12,Fand 34 votes against, a result
OL,13,Fwelcomed by the leaders of the council.
OL,15,FPro- and anti-immigration protestors
OL,16,Fpacked a Tuesday (January 13) meeting
OL,17,Fon the vote.
