OL,3,CPlans approved to make local authority
OL,4,Ca 'council of sanctuary'
OL,6,FCouncils, or places of sanctuary, take
OL,7,Fsteps to support people who seek
OL,8,Fsanctuary, such as refugees,
OL,9,Fimmigrants, and those fleeing domestic
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FCarlisle was made a city of sanctuary
OL,13,Fin 2024, and in a council debate on
OL,14,FNovember 25, 2025, Cumberland Council
OL,15,Fadopted a statement of sanctuary for
OL,16,Fthe whole council area.
