OL,6,FSo many members of the public attended
OL,7,Fthe meeting that security had to close
OL,8,Fthe doors on some to avoid
OL,9,Fovercrowding, while more protesters
OL,10,Fgathered outside.
OL,12,FCllr Lisa Hinton told ITV Border: "It
OL,13,Fwas a really good debate. Lots and
OL,14,Flots of people have turned up. So it
OL,15,Fwas really good to see democracy in
OL,16,Faction.
