OL,3,CPlans approved to make local authority
OL,4,Ca 'council of sanctuary'
OL,6,F"We (will) carry on with the place of
OL,7,Fsanctuary work, making sure that the
OL,8,Fthings that we've added in the support
OL,9,Ffor domestic abuse - we're working
OL,10,Fwith Cumberland Domestic Abuse
OL,11,FStrategy Framework and all of those
OL,12,Fpeople, as well as asylum seeker and
OL,13,Frefugee support groups."
OL,15,FOne of the councillors opposing the
OL,16,Fidea, Cllr Gareth Ellis, said
OL,17,Fsanctuary status would encourage more
OL,18,Fpeople to come to the UK.
