OL,4,Ca 'council of sanctuary'
OL,6,FCllr Ellis said: "The problem is that
OL,7,Fthe Place of Sanctuary Network, which
OL,8,Fis a national network, is one of those
OL,9,Fthings that the Home Office call a
OL,10,F'pull factor'.
OL,12,F"It encourages people to come to the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom. It encourages people
OL,14,Fto cross over from Calais. We've had
OL,15,F50,000 people come in and they're
OL,16,Fcoming because the smugglers tell
OL,17,Fthem, come to the UK, look what it's
OL,18,Flike."
