OL,3,CPlans approved to make local authority
OL,4,Ca 'council of sanctuary'
OL,6,FSupporters say the sanctuary scheme
OL,7,Fwould help provide proper plans to
OL,8,Fdeal with refugees and asylum seekers,
OL,9,Fand bring in charities and other
OL,10,Forganisations to help.
OL,12,FSome of those opposed to the idea say
OL,13,Fit will encourage more migrants to
OL,14,Fsettle in Cumbria.
OL,16,FHome Office figures show there were
OL,17,F508 asylum seekers in Cumbria in 2025.
